information.title: The Magical Revolution of the Reincarnated Princess and the Genius Young Lady
information.synopsis: There’s one thing Anis can’t go without if she wants to advance magicology in the Kingdom of Palettia—spirit stones. Fortunately, an untamed region to the east is teeming with this vital resource, so she and Euphie decide to journey by air to stock up and survey the land for future development. Euphie has an itinerary of new and interesting places to visit along the way—wait, does this count as a honeymoon?!
